This paper analyzes the language used by users in echo chambers on Facebook, which involves natural language processing and social network analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also deals with social networks and polarization, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SD (Software Engineering and Security). Additionally, the paper touches upon social psychology and communication, which could be categorized under cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences) and cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity and Privacy).
